WEBVTT

00:06.640 --> 00:09.143
PREVIOUSLY ON
"UNITED STATES OF TARA"...

00:09.177 --> 00:10.244
HOW MANY PEOPLE
AT YOUR PARTY?

00:10.278 --> 00:11.479
AROUND 30.
LESS THAN 10.

00:11.512 --> 00:13.047
THE SHOWER IS ON SUNDAY.
YOU PROMISED.

00:13.081 --> 00:14.648
"OH, MY GOD.
I FUCKED UP YOUR WEDDING.

00:14.682 --> 00:16.517
LET ME MAKE IT UP TO YOU" --
THAT'S WHAT SHE SAID.

00:16.550 --> 00:18.552
I WAS JUST ACCEPTED
TO THE PROGRAM,

00:18.586 --> 00:21.555
AND I'M BACK AT SCHOOL FOR THE
FIRST TIME SINCE THE EARLY '90s.

00:21.589 --> 00:24.225
I'M DR. SHOSHANA SCHOENBAUM.

00:24.258 --> 00:28.096
TRUST ME --
YOU WI BE STIMULATED.

00:28.129 --> 00:30.398
"BOYFRIEND" IS JUST ANOTHER ONE
OF THOSE GROSS WORDS,

00:30.431 --> 00:33.267
LIKE "VAGINA"
OR "LOVE."

00:33.301 --> 00:35.436
ST. LOUIS TO SAN FRANCISCO,
SAN FRANCISCO TO OSAKA.

00:35.469 --> 00:36.770
I'M GOING THERE
TO TEACH ENGLISH.

00:36.804 --> 00:38.239
YOU SAID OSAKA,
RIGHT?

00:38.272 --> 00:39.573
YES.

00:41.542 --> 00:43.811
DO YOU HAVE ANY CITIES

00:43.844 --> 00:45.846
THAT YOU NEED
ENGLISH-SPEAKING TEACHERS?

00:45.879 --> 00:48.216
DON'T THROW THOSE OUT.
YOUR FATHER LOVES THOSE DUCKS.

00:48.249 --> 00:49.817
BET YOU ALL THE MONEY I HAVE,
THE DAY HE LEFT,

00:49.850 --> 00:52.453
HE TOOK ONE LOOK AT THAT BOX,
KNEW WHAT WAS INSIDE,

00:52.486 --> 00:55.289
AND SAID, "FUCK THIS,"
AND TOOK OFF.

00:55.323 --> 00:57.091
DO YOU EVER THINK
ABOUT TAKING OFF?

00:57.125 --> 00:58.559
WHAT CITY IN JAPAN?
[ SIGHS ] NIIGATA.

00:58.592 --> 00:59.727
OH, DEAR.

00:59.760 --> 01:01.629
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"OH, DEAR"?

01:01.662 --> 01:03.464
WHY DID SHE SAY "OH, DEAR"?

01:03.497 --> 01:04.732
[ GASPS ]

01:04.765 --> 01:06.300
MA'AM,
IS SOMETHING WRONG?

01:06.334 --> 01:08.336
TARA!
IT'S T!

01:08.369 --> 01:10.704
YOU WILL NOT DO THIS TO ME
AGAIN! YOU WILL COME BACK!

01:11.772 --> 01:13.374
WHAT THE FUCK?

01:13.407 --> 01:15.309
[ ENGINE REVS ]
TARA!

01:15.343 --> 01:16.710
OH, SHIT.

01:18.612 --> 01:20.414
[ SIREN WAILING ]

01:20.448 --> 01:21.649
ALL RIGHT,
GOOD CONTRACTIONS.

01:21.682 --> 01:23.117
YOU'RE DOING
GOOD THERE, TARA.

01:23.151 --> 01:24.818
I'M NOT TARA,
YOU FUCKING MORON.

01:24.852 --> 01:28.189
THE ONE WITH THE BABY
POKING OUT OF HER IS CHARMAINE.

01:28.222 --> 01:29.557
THE ONE WHO RAN THE BABY OVER
IS SISTER TARA.

01:29.590 --> 01:31.125
OW.

01:31.159 --> 01:32.693
HI. I-I DIDN'T ACTUALLY
RUN HER OVER.

01:32.726 --> 01:34.595
DON'T LISTEN TO HER,
BECAUSE SHE WASN'T THERE,

01:34.628 --> 01:36.564
BECAUSE SHE WASN'T SHE,
BECAUSE SHE'S FUCKING CRAZY!

01:36.597 --> 01:38.766
I'M NOT CRAZY.

01:38.799 --> 01:40.901
I'M SORRY. WHAT'S THE
PROPER MEDICAL TERM
FOR "BATSHIT INSANE"?

01:40.934 --> 01:43.337
SO, YOU TWO
ARE SISTERS.
[ Laughing ]
I DON'T KNOW.

01:43.371 --> 01:45.873
HOW YOU CAN BE SISTERS
WITH SOMEONE WHO'S GOT
42 PEOPLE IN HER HEAD

01:45.906 --> 01:47.475
WHO KEEP TRYING
TO RUIN YOUR LIFE?

01:47.508 --> 01:48.742
MY WEDDING, OKAY?

01:48.776 --> 01:49.743
[ Imitating Chicken ]
"I SO SLEEPY!"

01:49.777 --> 01:50.744
OW! OW!

01:50.778 --> 01:51.912
DISASTER.

01:51.945 --> 01:53.281
FULL-ON, FERAL SPAZ-OUT
AT THE --

01:53.314 --> 01:55.883
OW, OW, OW, OW! -- SPA.

01:55.916 --> 01:56.884
AWESOME.

01:56.917 --> 01:58.252
OH, MY NEW BREASTS?

01:58.286 --> 01:59.620
[ LAUGHS ]

01:59.653 --> 02:01.189
CREEPTASTIC MOMENT THERE.

02:01.222 --> 02:02.756
BUT THIS -- OW, OW --
THIS -- OW --

02:02.790 --> 02:04.325
THIS TOPS THE CHARTS.

02:04.358 --> 02:06.360
AND PREMATURE LABOR
INDUCED VIA VOLKSWAGEN?!

02:06.394 --> 02:08.329
I DON'T KNOW HOW
YOU'RE GONNA TOP THAT ONE, TARA.

02:08.362 --> 02:09.697
OW.

02:09.730 --> 02:11.332
LOOK, I AM SORRY.
I DIDN'T MEAN TO --

02:11.365 --> 02:13.634
I JUST WANTED
A GODDAMN BABY SHOWER!

02:13.667 --> 02:15.469
LISTEN, EVERYTHING IS
GOING TO BE FINE.

02:15.503 --> 02:17.838
ONE DAY, THIS'LL BE A WACKY
STORY WE TELL OUR GRANDCHILDREN.

02:17.871 --> 02:19.507
NO, I'M DONE
LAUGHING THIS OFF.

02:19.540 --> 02:22.910
I AM GOING TO HAVE MY BABY
IN A NORMAL FUCKING WAY,

02:22.943 --> 02:25.779
WITH NORMAL FUCKING PEOPLE
AROUND ME.

02:25.813 --> 02:27.881
STAY AWAY FROM ME.
YOU ARE NOT FUCKING THIS UP.
NO, I HEAR
WHAT YOU'RE SAYING.

02:27.915 --> 02:29.650
AAH!

02:29.683 --> 02:31.552
OH, GOD, BE CAREFUL WITH HER!
CHARMAINE, CHARMAINE!

02:31.585 --> 02:33.487
PLEASE KEEP HER AWAY FROM ME.
SHE'S FUCKING CRAZY, OKAY?

02:33.521 --> 02:34.955
OH, I'M SO SORRY.
I'M SORRY.

02:34.988 --> 02:36.890
KEEP HER AWAY FROM ME.
SHE'S FUCKING CRAZY.

02:36.924 --> 02:38.926
AAAAAH! AAH!

02:38.959 --> 02:40.794
IT WAS PRETTY INTENSE.

02:40.828 --> 02:42.630
I MEAN, IT'S A LOT GOING ON --
VERY HARD TO EXPLAIN.

02:42.663 --> 02:43.664
SORT OF REALLY INTENSE.

02:43.697 --> 02:45.199
YEAH,
YOU SAID "INTENSE."

02:45.233 --> 02:47.601
THIS BURSTING FORTH
OF -- OF -- OF REALIZA--

02:47.635 --> 02:50.338
OR, NO, OF THIS -- THIS --
THIS SUDDEN BIG BANG

02:50.371 --> 02:52.406
OF CONSCIOUSNESS,
LIKE -- LIKE BOOM!

02:52.440 --> 02:54.208
NEW UNIVERSE OF KATE.

02:54.242 --> 02:56.210
MEG SAID
YOU FREAKED THE FUCK OUT.

02:56.244 --> 02:57.545
[ GROANS ]

02:57.578 --> 02:59.347
JUNIN TOIRO,
WHICH -- WHICH MEANS

02:59.380 --> 03:02.683
"DIFFERENT STROKES
TO MOVE THE WORLD."

03:02.716 --> 03:04.852
IS THAT YOURS?

03:04.885 --> 03:06.454
[ GASPS ]

03:06.487 --> 03:07.455
OHHHH!

03:07.488 --> 03:09.390
[ SIGHS ]

03:09.423 --> 03:12.226
WELL, HERE'S ONE.
WHERE'S THE OTHER BAG?

03:12.260 --> 03:13.961
JAPAN?

03:13.994 --> 03:15.963
BURSTING
INTO CONSCIOUSNESS?

03:15.996 --> 03:19.633
THE POSSIBILITIES
ARE VARIED AND COMPLEX.

03:19.667 --> 03:22.736
WELL...COULD YOU...
FIGURE IT OUT?

03:22.770 --> 03:24.572
IT HURTS MY BRAIN
WHEN I GIVE A SHIT.

03:24.605 --> 03:26.006
[ SCOFFS ]
COME ON, RAY.

03:26.039 --> 03:27.641
CAN'T YOU SEE
THAT I AM IN THE MIDDLE

03:27.675 --> 03:29.243
OF SOME LIFE-ALTERING STUFF
RIGHT NOW,

03:29.277 --> 03:30.911
STUFF THAT I HAVE YET
TO SPRING ON MY PARENTS,

03:30.944 --> 03:33.914
AND IT WOULD BE A REALLY BIG,
MAJOR, SUPER-HELPFUL THING

03:33.947 --> 03:37.251
IF I HAD MY SHIT TOGETHER,
SO TO SPEAK?

03:37.285 --> 03:38.352
PLEASE?

03:38.386 --> 03:40.388
I WOULD PREFER NOT TO.

03:40.421 --> 03:42.690
KACHOFUGETSU.

03:42.723 --> 03:44.592
"FLOWER, BIRD,
WIND, MOON."

03:44.625 --> 03:45.993
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

03:46.026 --> 03:48.896
I DON'T KNOW,
BUT IT SOUNDS PRETTY.

03:48.929 --> 03:50.831
HEY,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

03:50.864 --> 03:52.600
[ As Alice ]
OH, I'M JUST PEACHY.

03:52.633 --> 03:55.436
I'M QUITE FOND OF HOSPITALS.
THEY'RE VERY CLEAN.

03:55.469 --> 03:57.605
GREAT. GREAT.
FANTASTIC...ALICE.

03:57.638 --> 03:58.972
I NEED TARA.

03:59.006 --> 04:01.442
OH. SHE'S A TAD OVERWHELMED
RIGHT NOW.

04:01.475 --> 04:03.611
I NEED TO TALK TO TARA.

04:03.644 --> 04:05.779
FORTUNATELY,
I'M PRACTICALLY A MIDWIFE,

04:05.813 --> 04:08.616
READY TO HELP CHARMAINE
THROUGH THE MIRACLE OF BIRTH.

04:08.649 --> 04:10.618
YEAH, I HEAR T FUCKED UP
THE MIRACLE OF BIRTH --

04:10.651 --> 04:13.587
AND THE CAR, WHICH IS WHY
I WANT TO TALK TO MY WIFE.

04:13.621 --> 04:14.888
WE ARE ABOUT TO WITNESS

04:14.922 --> 04:17.291
A BEAUTIFUL
AND LIFE-CHANGING EVENT, MAX.

04:17.325 --> 04:18.992
DAD, UM...
THERE'S AN ANGRY COP OUTSIDE

04:19.026 --> 04:20.894
WANTS A WORD.

04:20.928 --> 04:23.531
WHEN YOU SEE TARA, TELL HER
I'M FEELING "A TAD OVERWHELMED."

04:29.603 --> 04:30.571
[ SIGHS ]

04:30.604 --> 04:31.772
[ As Tara ] HI.

04:31.805 --> 04:33.907
HI.

04:33.941 --> 04:37.445
SO...

04:37.478 --> 04:39.480
HOW'S GRANDMA SANDY?

04:39.513 --> 04:41.749
OH, YOU KNOW --
OLD, SCARED,

04:41.782 --> 04:44.818
CLINGING TO A LIFE
THAT NO LONGER EXISTS.

04:44.852 --> 04:46.920
HOW ARE YOU?

04:46.954 --> 04:48.356
JUST PEACHY.

04:48.389 --> 04:49.923
AAAAH!

04:49.957 --> 04:51.659
Doctor:
OKAY, MISS CRAINE.

04:51.692 --> 04:53.361
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

04:53.394 --> 04:55.829
PROMISE ME
YOU'LL LET ME NAME HER.

04:55.863 --> 04:57.965
WHAT? NO, NO, NO.
YOU'LL PICK SOMETHING STUPID.

04:57.998 --> 04:59.700
CASSANDRA IS
A BEAUTIFUL NAME!

04:59.733 --> 05:00.801
IT HAS THE WORD "ASS"
IN IT.

05:00.834 --> 05:01.969
AAAH!

05:02.002 --> 05:03.837
PROMISE ME, NEIL.
YOU OWE ME.

05:03.871 --> 05:05.439
BABY'S HEAD
MIGHT BE TOO BIG.

05:05.473 --> 05:06.974
WHAT?! SEE?!

05:07.007 --> 05:09.977
THIS IS ALL YOUR FAULT, YOU AND
THAT GIANT SKULL OF YOURS!

05:10.010 --> 05:11.111
AAAAH!

05:11.144 --> 05:13.347
LET -- LET --
LET ME SEE.

05:13.381 --> 05:14.982
OKAY, WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON DOWN THERE?

05:15.015 --> 05:17.485
IT LOOKS LIKE ABE LINCOLN
AFTER HE GOT SHOT IN THE FACE.

05:17.518 --> 05:19.953
WHAT?! I WILL GET YOU
FOR THIS, NEIL.

05:19.987 --> 05:22.523
I WILL POUND YOUR BALLS
TILL THEY SWELL UP LIKE MELONS

05:22.556 --> 05:24.091
AND YOU HAVE TO CARRY THEM
AROUND IN A TESTICLE BJORN.

05:24.124 --> 05:25.626
AAAAH!

05:25.659 --> 05:26.927
ALL RIGHT, MAMA,
WE'RE GONNA TAKE YOU

05:26.960 --> 05:28.796
DOWN TO THE O.R.,
GET THIS BABY OUT.

05:28.829 --> 05:30.464
E-EVERYTHING'S --
RELAX.
EVERYTHING'S FINE.

05:30.498 --> 05:32.132
WE JUST GOT A REAL BIG
BASKETBALL, REAL SMALL HOOP.

05:32.165 --> 05:34.034
W-WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?
SHE'S GETTING
A C-SECTION.

05:34.067 --> 05:35.736
AAAAH!
A C-SECTION?

05:35.769 --> 05:37.438
OKAY, OKAY.

05:37.471 --> 05:40.541
UH, HOLD TIGHT, MR. LINCOLN!
HELP IS ON THE WAY!

05:40.574 --> 05:42.743
OH. THANK YOU.

05:46.414 --> 05:48.682
ARE WE COMPLETELY SCREWED UP
AS A FAMILY?

05:48.716 --> 05:51.485
I MEAN...
ASIDE FROM OUR WACKY COUSINS

05:51.519 --> 05:53.854
THAT LIVE
INSIDE YOUR HEAD.

05:53.887 --> 05:55.756
WELL, TECHNICALLY,
YOU'RE NOT RELATED.

05:55.789 --> 05:56.857
[ CHUCKLES ]

05:56.890 --> 05:59.693
BUT...YOU, ME,
DAD, AND KATE --

05:59.727 --> 06:01.662
WE'RE...

06:01.695 --> 06:02.730
WE'RE OKAY, RIGHT?

06:02.763 --> 06:03.731
YEAH.

06:03.764 --> 06:04.832
WHY?

06:04.865 --> 06:06.900
I DON'T KNOW.
SOAP DUCKS.

06:08.068 --> 06:09.670
DUCKS MADE OF SOAP?

06:09.703 --> 06:12.406
NO --
SOAP MADE OF DUCKS.

06:12.440 --> 06:14.775
[ Chuckling ] HONEY, I DON'T
KNOW WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

06:16.744 --> 06:18.446
DO YOU THINK
DAD WOULD EVER LEAVE US?

06:18.479 --> 06:21.114
WHAT IF HE --
HE GOT TIRED OF THE...

06:21.148 --> 06:23.016
US?

06:23.050 --> 06:25.619
OH, HE'S -- [SCOFFS]
HE'S NOT GOING ANYWHERE. HE'S...

06:30.691 --> 06:32.726
YOU KNOW YOU WERE BORN
IN THIS HOSPITAL?

06:32.760 --> 06:34.862
KATE, TOO.

06:34.895 --> 06:37.030
GOD, SHE WAS TOUGH,
BUT YOU --

06:37.064 --> 06:40.901
YOU POPPED RIGHT OUT,
STRAIGHT INTO MY ARMS.

06:40.934 --> 06:44.738
WERE YOU...YOU
WHEN YOU HAD US?

06:44.772 --> 06:47.741
I MEAN, YOU WEREN'T BUCK
OR -- OR ALICE?

06:47.775 --> 06:49.510
OH, CAN YOU IMAGINE?
GOD, BUCK?

06:49.543 --> 06:50.511
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:50.544 --> 06:51.845
SERIOUSLY.

06:51.879 --> 06:54.482
WAS EVERYTHING NORMAL
WHEN YOU HAD US?

06:54.515 --> 06:57.585
EVERYTHING WAS FINE,
MOOSH.

06:57.618 --> 07:00.688
EVERYTHING IS FINE.

07:00.721 --> 07:03.056
QUITE AN ADVENTURE YOU HAD
BACK THERE AT FIELD'S MARKET.

07:03.090 --> 07:04.925
THEY HAVE REALLY GOOD
SHEET CAKE.

07:04.958 --> 07:07.027
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?
OH, YEAH.

07:07.060 --> 07:08.662
YOU JUST CRASHED
A COUPLE CARS

07:08.696 --> 07:10.764
AND STOLE A BUNCH OF STUFF
FROM THE STORE.

07:12.600 --> 07:14.034
I HAVE A BABY.

07:14.067 --> 07:15.035
[ GASPS ]

07:15.068 --> 07:16.937
A MOTHERFUCKING BABY!

07:16.970 --> 07:18.872
IT LOOKS LIKE CRAP --

07:18.906 --> 07:22.543
DISGUSTING, BLOOD-DRIPPING,
FUCKING RAISIN MONSTER --

07:22.576 --> 07:25.646
BUT IT IS A MOTHERFUCKING BABY,
AND IT'S MINE!

07:25.679 --> 07:27.247
[ LAUGHTER ]
WHOO!

07:27.280 --> 07:29.883
[ BABY COOS ]

07:29.917 --> 07:31.552
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

07:31.585 --> 07:32.920
UH-HUH.

07:32.953 --> 07:35.856
SEE THAT?
I DID THAT.

07:35.889 --> 07:38.258
BRAVO, GUYS.

07:38.291 --> 07:39.993
THANK YOU, GOD,
FOR MAKING ME GAY.

07:40.027 --> 07:42.062
[ SNEEZES ]

07:42.095 --> 07:43.864
OH, BLESS YOU.
KAH-CHOO!

07:43.897 --> 07:45.165
DO YOU HAVE A NAME?

07:45.198 --> 07:46.834
WE'RE KICKING
SOME IDEAS AROUND.

07:46.867 --> 07:48.502
CASSANDRA.

07:48.536 --> 07:51.138
WHICH IS MY FAVORITE --
ABSOLUTELY.

07:51.171 --> 07:52.973
HEY, CAN UNCLE MAX
HAVE A SNUGGLE?

07:53.006 --> 07:54.808
YES, UNCLE MAX
CAN HAVE A SNUGGLE

07:54.842 --> 07:56.544
AFTER UNCLE MAX
WASHES HIS HANDS.

07:56.577 --> 07:58.278
SAME WITH YOU,
COUSIN WHAT'S-HIS-NAME.

07:58.311 --> 07:59.547
AND YOU'RE NEXT,
AUNT TARA.

07:59.580 --> 08:00.548
YEAH.

08:00.581 --> 08:02.049
OH.

08:02.082 --> 08:05.719
I DON'T...REALLY THINK
THAT'S A GOOD IDEA.

08:05.753 --> 08:07.755
NO, DOCTOR SAID
IT'S OKAY, BABY.

08:07.788 --> 08:09.857
Tara: I COULD JUST...

08:09.890 --> 08:11.892
I MEAN,
EVERYONE'S RIGHT HERE.

08:11.925 --> 08:14.261
I COULD JUST...
HOLD HER FOR A SECOND.

08:14.294 --> 08:17.030
I'M REALLY NOT COMFORTABLE
WITH THIS RIGHT NOW.

08:17.064 --> 08:19.166
[ Voice breaking ]
THAT WAS T. IT WASN'T ME.

08:19.199 --> 08:21.669
I DON'T WANT YOU IN HERE
WITH THE BABY, TARA.

08:21.702 --> 08:23.537
OKAY, LET'S --
LET'S JUST GO OUTSIDE --

08:23.571 --> 08:24.805
NO, I --

08:24.838 --> 08:26.106
COME ON, BABE.
NO.

08:33.146 --> 08:35.583
Noah: WHO THE HELL
DRINKS SCHNAPPS?

08:35.616 --> 08:37.284
Marshall and Lionel:
NEIL.

08:37.317 --> 08:39.219
I DON'T GET BABIES.

08:39.252 --> 08:42.122
WELL, WHAT'S TO GET?
THEY'RE LITTLE PEOPLE.

08:42.155 --> 08:43.824
MIDGETS
ARE LITTLE PEOPLE.

08:43.857 --> 08:46.560
BABIES ARE
INCONTINENT EXTENSIONS

08:46.594 --> 08:48.929
OF THE ADULT DESIRE
TO REWRITE HISTORY.

08:48.962 --> 08:51.198
I LOVE HOW YOU CAN BE
SO PRETENTIOUS

08:51.231 --> 08:53.767
AND SO COMPLETELY STUPID
AT THE SAME TIME.

08:53.801 --> 08:54.968
WHAT?

08:55.002 --> 08:57.605
RANDOM PEOPLE
MASH TOGETHER,

08:57.638 --> 08:59.873
AND THEN THEY CHUNK OUT KIDS
INSTEAD OF DEALING WITH THE FACT

08:59.907 --> 09:02.009
THEY SHOULD NEVER HAVE BEEN
TOGETHER IN THE FIRST PLACE.

09:02.042 --> 09:03.877
YOU THINK
THEY HAVE ANY PORN?

09:03.911 --> 09:06.880
THAT'S HOW YOU RESPOND?

09:06.914 --> 09:09.850
WELL, WE CAN'T FIND ANY VODKA,
SO...YEAH.

09:10.918 --> 09:12.185
[ GASPS ]

09:12.219 --> 09:13.854
BEST THREESOMES
IN MOVIES. GO.

09:13.887 --> 09:14.855
"JULES ET JIM."

09:14.888 --> 09:16.356
MM-HMM.

09:16.389 --> 09:18.592
SEE? THAT'S WHAT
I'M TALKING ABOUT.

09:18.626 --> 09:19.893
IT'S AN IMPORTANT FILM.

09:19.927 --> 09:21.795
DON'T KNOW
WHAT'S MORE DEPRESSING --

09:21.829 --> 09:23.230
FRENCH CINEMA

09:23.263 --> 09:27.635
OR THAT I'M CHUGGING
80-PROOF MOUTHWASH.

09:27.668 --> 09:29.770
FUCK YOU, WORLD.

09:31.404 --> 09:32.906
[ Laughing ] HEY.

09:32.940 --> 09:34.908
NIIGATA,
YOU'RE STILL HERE.

09:34.942 --> 09:36.209
PILOT STILL DRUNK?

09:36.243 --> 09:38.812
NO. I, UH...

09:38.846 --> 09:40.914
I-I...JUST COULDN'T.

09:40.948 --> 09:42.716
OH, DEAR.

09:42.750 --> 09:45.352
IN 12 HOURS, I'M SUPPOSED TO
CALL MY PARENTS FROM JAPAN

09:45.385 --> 09:47.655
TO TELL THEM
HOW AWESOME MY NEW LIFE IS.

09:47.688 --> 09:49.823
HOW BAD
IS YOUR OLD LIFE?

09:49.857 --> 09:51.959
HEY, DO YOU THINK
THAT MAYBE I COULD FAKE IT,

09:51.992 --> 09:56.263
LIKE I COULD PRETEND TO BE
IN JAPAN FOR SIX MONTHS?

09:56.296 --> 09:58.666
I FAKED HAVING ORGASMS
FOR SIX YEARS.

09:58.699 --> 10:01.635
THEN I STOPPED NURTURING
A BLIND HATRED FOR MY LIFE

10:01.669 --> 10:04.271
AND GOT DIVORCED.

10:04.304 --> 10:06.707
THERE'S A LESSON IN THERE
SOMEWHERE.

10:06.740 --> 10:08.876
THE BIG "O"
IS LIFE.

10:08.909 --> 10:10.911
YOU CAN FAKE YOUR WAY
THROUGH IT,

10:10.944 --> 10:12.746
BUT WHAT'S
THE FUCKING POINT?

10:22.022 --> 10:24.257
SHE'S A FUCKING GENIUS.

10:24.291 --> 10:27.928
* DON'T WALK AWAY

10:27.961 --> 10:31.999
* ANGEL OF DECEPTION

