I JUST WANT YOU TO BE SAFE.

22:16.803 --> 22:18.605
I WANT YOU TO DO THINGS
THAT MAKE SENSE,

22:18.638 --> 22:21.674
NOT THAT ARE...CRAZY!

22:21.708 --> 22:24.076
YOU ARE NOT SUCH
A FUCKING SAINT, ARE YOU?

22:24.110 --> 22:26.979
WHY DON'T YOU JUST...

22:27.013 --> 22:30.483
JUST LEAVE, JUST...

22:30.517 --> 22:32.752
JUST WALK AWAY,
LIKE YOUR DAD?

22:39.125 --> 22:41.027
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU.

22:42.729 --> 22:45.465
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

22:45.498 --> 22:46.833
OHH!

22:46.866 --> 22:49.902
ALL OF THIS STOPS RIGHT NOW --
RIGHT NOW.

22:49.936 --> 22:53.506
NO MORE SELFISHNESS,
NO MORE HIJACKING,

22:53.540 --> 22:56.709
NO MORE EXCUSES,
AND NO MORE PASSING THE BUCK.

22:56.743 --> 22:58.177
[ LAUGHS ]
OH, SHUT UP.

22:58.210 --> 23:01.681
FROM NOW ON,
MY LIFE WILL BE ORGANIZED --

23:01.714 --> 23:05.852
MY LIFE, MY LIBERTY,
MY PURSUIT OF HAPPINESS.

23:05.885 --> 23:08.087
THESE THINGS
WILL BEND TO MY WILL.

23:08.120 --> 23:10.490
I WILL BE IN CONTROL --
ME, TARA.

23:10.523 --> 23:11.891
END OF STORY.

23:11.924 --> 23:14.193
I AM SICK AND TIRED
OF ALL THE CRAZINESS.

23:14.226 --> 23:15.895
THIS IS ALL YOUR FAULT, WITH
THE DRUGS AND THE BLACK MUSIC.

23:15.928 --> 23:17.530
EAT ME, STEPFORD.

23:17.564 --> 23:19.699
BUCK HAD THE BIG NIGHT OUT.
I WASN'T EVEN --

23:19.732 --> 23:21.634
HEY, I WAS DOIN'
IMPORTANT STUFF.

23:21.668 --> 23:23.202
JUST HAPPENED TO BE
AT A CASINO.

23:23.235 --> 23:26.573
I, FOR ONE, THINK IT'S ABOUT
TIME YOU ASSERTED YOURSELF.

23:26.606 --> 23:27.674
ABSOLUTELY.
IT'S A WONDERFUL --

23:27.707 --> 23:29.041
JUST SHUT THE FUCK UP!

23:29.075 --> 23:30.643
[ As Chicken ] OOH!
TARA, YOU SAID THE "F" WORD.

23:30.677 --> 23:31.911
[ SIGHS ]

23:31.944 --> 23:34.080
CAN WE JUST DROWN HER?
AND THE DOG?

23:34.113 --> 23:35.982
[ GROWLS ]
OW! FUCK!

23:36.015 --> 23:36.983
GOOD, GIMME!
FUCK YOU!

23:37.016 --> 23:38.718
[ GROWLS ]

23:38.751 --> 23:41.688
I HAVE SPENT FAR TOO LONG
BABYING YOU -- ALL OF YOU.

23:41.721 --> 23:43.189
YOU ACT LIKE
SPOILED BRATS,

23:43.222 --> 23:45.492
AND THEN YOU LEAVE ME
HOLDING THE BAG.

23:45.525 --> 23:48.795
SO, WE ARE GOING TO DRAW UP
A CONTRACT.

23:48.828 --> 23:50.863
ALL OF YOU WILL WRITE DOWN
WHAT'S IMPORTANT TO YOU

23:50.897 --> 23:52.532
AND WHAT YOU WANT
OUT OF LIFE,

23:52.565 --> 23:55.835
AND THEN I, AND I ALONE,
WILL DECIDE HOW WE GO ABOUT IT.

23:55.868 --> 23:57.637
DON'T SOUND LIKE
NO DEMOCRACY TO ME.

23:57.670 --> 23:59.238
[ Imitating Buck ]
WELL, IT AIN'T.

23:59.271 --> 24:03.643
[ Normal voice ] I AM DISSOLVING
THE UNITED STATES OF TARA

24:03.676 --> 24:05.578
AND DECLARING MYSELF KING.

24:05.612 --> 24:08.715
AND IF'N Y'ALL DON'T LIKE IT,
YOU CAN KISS MY ASS,

24:08.748 --> 24:10.216
'CAUSE I'LL GO BACK
ON THE DRUGS,

24:10.249 --> 24:11.984
AND YOU'LL GO BACK
IN THE CLOSET.

24:12.018 --> 24:13.486
WELL, THIS SUCKS.

24:14.821 --> 24:16.489
FINE.

24:16.523 --> 24:19.091
[ GRUNTING ]

24:20.993 --> 24:23.162
I NEED
MY BOOZIN' TIME.

24:23.195 --> 24:25.264
I NEED SOME TV TIME.

24:25.297 --> 24:27.099
I SWEAR,
NO MORE LADIES WITH US.

24:34.106 --> 24:36.075
THAT'S THE IMPORTANT ONE.

24:36.108 --> 24:37.977
[ LAUGHS ]

24:38.010 --> 24:39.946
BA-CHOO! POP!

24:42.014 --> 24:44.917
I HEREBY DECLARE
MY BENEVOLENT DICTATORSHIP

24:44.951 --> 24:47.119
TO BE IN FULL EFFECT.

24:47.153 --> 24:49.121
LONG LIVE THE KING!

24:53.993 --> 24:58.064
* MEETS ME IN A FIELD
OF STONE *

25:02.702 --> 25:07.106
* SHE SAYS, "I DON'T KNOW
HOW I'M SUPPOSED TO FEEL" *

25:12.044 --> 25:16.816
* MY BODY'S COLD,
MY GUTS ARE TWISTED STEEL *

25:19.786 --> 25:21.320
[ Voice breaking ]
I'M CRAZY.

25:21.353 --> 25:24.724
* AND I FEEL LIKE
I'M SOME KIND OF FRANKENSTEIN *

25:24.757 --> 25:26.693
I'M FUCKING CRAZY.

25:26.726 --> 25:31.263
* WAITING FOR A SHOCK
TO BRING ME BACK TO LIFE *

25:31.297 --> 25:36.903
* BUT I DON'T WANT TO SPEND
MY TIME *

25:36.936 --> 25:42.341
* WAITING FOR LIGHTNING
TO STRIKE *

25:42.374 --> 25:46.145
* OOOOH
